headline.print_headline: Investment Bank UBS to Outsource Fixed Income Trading Platform
headline.main: Investment Bank UBS to Outsource Fixed Income Trading Platform

lead_paragraph: Swiss bank UBS will begin outsourcing its fixed income trading platform to two technology groups in an attempt to save costs, a source told Reuters.
